{"tid":1563983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港注定玩完 根本冇人跳閘 講咩革命","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:48:50.000Z","uid":86086,"like":59,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4be4bc5ada4d8d44ae8daa4c329bb55bff65d1","tid":1563983,"uid":86086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:05:53.000Z","msg":"首先 <br />\n有跳比正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇跳比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟手就屌撚柒港豬<br />\n<br />\n你話我分化撚又好咩都好 我每個站都睇幾班車 根冇用人跳 幾班先得1，2個<br />\n唔好同我講咩革命啦 跳個閘都唔肯 都要驚 肯咩革命呀<br />\n721 831 叫哂口號都冇用 港豬冇得救<br />\n好多後生冇跳 中年 廢老我當唔計<br />\n係到話好多粉紅守住呀盛 <br />\n人地哂錢請咁多垃圾番黎擺你就比佢嚇到乖乖比錢<br />\nCctv唔肯交 比幾張圖當過骨？<br />\n唔肯跳閘既港豬 死左既義士同比人殺既人一定會搵你圾<br />\n跳閘既人唔多 唔會有力量 到時得一兩個跳 反而比人捉 話不割不分 全部廢話<br />\n我屌你地老母"},{"pid":"58d5115bdfb433c44db36f8716e6cb58ac9bbea4","tid":1563983,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3b0449973b4d908d10bcbdc26d1324e4413caacb","tid":1563983,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"有d野真係要慢慢黎<br />\n<br />\n[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"h